ason\": \"服务响应时间严重恶化，rrt_max的P99分位数增加96.06%，从27.86秒升至54.62秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max P99从27857.16ms升至54619.19ms，变化率96.06%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务响应时间异常，rrt和rrt_max同时出现显著增长，rrt P99增加96.05%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt P99从2773.73ms升至5436.08ms，变化率96.05%；rrt_max中位数增加45.13%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务错误率异常，error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99分位数均出现异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99变化率均为35.3%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务最大响应时间异常增长，rrt_max中位数增加13.79%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max中位数从10099ms升至11595ms，变化率13.79%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点总结：\n\n1. **节点级问题**：aiops-k8s-08节点内存可用性显著下降，可能成为系统性能瓶颈\n2. **服务级异常**：currencyservice和cartservice的多个实例出现严重的响应时间恶化\n3. **错误率异常**：cartservice-0出现错误率异常，需要关注服务稳定性\n4. **影响范围**：异常主要集中在aiops-k8s-08节点上的服务，包括currencyservice-2、cartservice-2等\n\n建议进入下一阶段深入分析这些异常组件之间的因果关系。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->EmailService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时显著增加，例如：hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote 从 9415.74ms 增加到 32018.79ms，hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder 从 14434.91ms 增加到 53521.57ms。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时显著增加，例如：hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder 从 237.89ms 增加到 1428.5ms。\"\